product.title: Lambert - The Olivia Vegan Leather Bag in Tan
product.body_html: A bag designed to never go unnoticed? Made with premium, PETA-certified vegan leather, the Olivia bag can easily be worn as a backpack or shoulder bag by adjusting the straps. Features multiple inside pockets for plenty of storage. 29.5cm (height) x 28cm (width) x 7.5cm (depth).
